blogPost.excerpt: Dual-pane file manager Commander One combines secure FTP client for Mac as well as cloud computing manager features and provides you with the built-in Mac Terminal emulator making it easy for you to manage all the system processes.
blogPost.body: Dual-pane file manager Commander One combines secure FTP client for Mac as well as cloud computing manager features and provides you with the built-in Mac Terminal emulator making it easy for you to manage all the system processes.
blogPost.title: Commander One 3.0 - Dual-pane file manager and FTP client for Mac
blogPost.author: Chris Messina

localize.description: 双窗格文件管理器Commander One结合了Mac的安全FTP客户端以及云计算管理器功能，并为您提供内置的Mac Terminal模拟器，使您可以轻松管理所有系统进程。
localize.tagline: Mac的双窗格文件管理器和FTP客户端

localize.description: 雙窗格文件管理器Commander One結合了Mac的安全FTP客戶端以及雲計算管理器功能，併爲您提供內置的Mac Terminal模擬器，使您可以輕鬆管理所有系統進程。
localize.tagline: Mac的雙窗格文件管理器和FTP客戶端
